1, getClass() is dynamic method, should not used in static void main()
Cannot make a static reference to the non-static method getClass() from the type Object

2, for main methods
It should define the main method as:
   public static void main(String[] args)
 
 
 
    slf4j-api-1.7.28.jar_______________for methods
    slf4j-simple-1.7.28.jar____________for binding
    
  3,when using other class---------> change the main function to other name, then refer to it.
